/i18n/other-engines\">Other Translation Engines</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/intro\">Rendering Strategies</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/build-state\">Build State</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/build-paths\">Build Paths</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/request-state\">Request State</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/revalidation\">Revalidation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/incremental\">Incremental Generation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/strategies/amalgamation\">State Amalgamation</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/hydration\">Hydration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/cli\">CLI</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/ejecting\">Ejecting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/snooping\">Snooping</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/testing/intro\">Testing</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/testing/checkpoints\">Checkpoints</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/testing/fantoccini-basics\">Fantoccini Basics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/testing/manual\">Manual Testing</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/styling\">Styling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://arctic-hen7.github.io/perseus/en-US/docs/next/server-communication\">Communicating with a Server</a>